Index of US Industrial Production

Source: R/datasets.R
us_indus_prod.Rd

Index of US industrial production (1985 = 100).

data(us_indus_prod)

Format

A data frame with 256 rows and 3 variables

Details

This is a transformation into simple data.frame of data USProdIndex in package 'AER'.
